                   <node depth="18" type="StaticText" id="" name="Customers find these curtains visually appealing, with one noting how the print adds a vintage touch, and many describing them as looking expensive. Moreover, the curtains are well-made, with one customer mentioning the quality and color exceeded expectations, and feature a bright white valance. Additionally, they effectively block out light while letting in just enough natural light, and customers appreciate their value for money. The fabric receives positive feedback for its linen-like texture and feel, and customers like its weight, with one noting it's heavy enough to hang perfectly." value="Customers find these curtains visually appealing, with one noting how the print adds a vintage touch, and many describing them as looking expensive. Moreover, the curtains are well-made, with one customer mentioning the quality and color exceeded expectations, and feature a bright white valance. Additionally, they effectively block out light while letting in just enough natural light, and customers appreciate their value for money. The fabric receives positive feedback for its linen-like texture and feel, a" label="Customers find these curtains visually appealing, with one noting how the print adds a vintage touch, and many describing them as looking expensive. Moreover, the curtains are well-made, with one customer mentioning the quality and color exceeded expectations, and feature a bright white valance. Additionally, they effectively block out light while letting in just enough natural light, and customers appreciate their value for money. The fabric receives positive feedback for its linen-like texture and feel, and customers like its weight, with one noting it's heavy enough to hang perfectly." enable="true" accessible="true" selected="false" index="304" visible="false" x="40" y="17962" width="756" height="480" bounds="[40,17962][796,18442]" nid="9224878128155QJTI" childcount="0" left="40" top="17962" rig